title: Smallville - Alien 008 (2014) (Digital) (JK-Empire)
description:
Written by: Bryan Q. Miller
Pencils: Edgar Salazar 
Cover by: Cat Staggs

The hit CW show has ended, but the Smallville story continues. Superman has revealed his alien heritage, but will the people of Earth still accept him?

Nightwing and Lois search Gotham for clues about the mysterious arrival of the wannabe superhero who was beaten to death. Clark and Lex explore the cavern they found in the Russian countryside, on the way to Chernobyl!
